<p><strong>特殊收容措施：</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">“睚眦”协议</span></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">/cn1998/protocol/yazi.pro&nbsp;&gt;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
